article.headline: Coppin St. 72, Allen 61
article.story: DOVER, Del. (AP) -- Tywain McKee scored 16 points to lead four Coppin State players in double figures as the Eagle beat Allen 72-61 SAturday in the Delaware State University Round Ball Classic. Vince Goldsberry finished with 13 points, while Antwain Harrison and Eddie Hayden added 10 each for Coppin State (2-0). John Doctor led all scorers with 27 points for Allen (0-5). Hiram Carolina added double-double performance with 16 points and 16 rebounds for the Yellow Jackets.
